{"tid":893452,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角好多假問卷真sales..","createTime":"2018-11-07T15:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T11:30:18.000Z","uid":71325,"like":454,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"624d5360951bf50ec8734b80234fa0c4917f9f2e","tid":893452,"uid":71325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:40:43.000Z","msg":"話說今日放學行過旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係地鐵站外面比人叫住左<br />\n叫幫手填份問卷<br />\n話自己好慘差一個人乜乜乜<br />\n求下我幫佢做返份<br />\n之後佢話做問卷要上佢樓上間健身室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n衰心軟上左去<br />\n<br />\n一上到去就問d簡單資料<br />\n然後開始話你腰伸唔直有駝背啊<br />\n邊個位唔好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就開始sell自己d健身plan<br />\n塞埋張介紹比我<br />\n我愈聽愈唔耐煩飛返張紙比佢調頭就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實就係呢類人愈黎愈多<br />\n真係想人做問卷個d應該都食愈多檸檬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次先有個fd比人sell到簽埋約<br />\n無左2萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以真係小心啲 唔好比人呃到<br />\n而且我見做緊份工嘅多數係青年<br />\n年輕人 有咩驅使你正常工唔返 返埋d狗工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5661be4a9d76c917ff2b2667d7cc52343174d4","tid":893452,"uid":219784,"like":200,"dislike":0,"score":200,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:46:44.000Z","msg":"依啲正仆街嚟嘅，專利用人哋嘅同情心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你個frd有冇追翻筆錢？"},{"pid":"8e6075bb855f36d4390d7ab869008eb08e7ebfaf","tid":893452,"uid":71325,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"0d5661be4a9d76c917ff2b2667d7cc52343174d4","tid":893452,"uid":219784,"like":200,"dislike":0,"score":200,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:46:44.000Z","msg