ts/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就開始sell自己d健身plan<br />\n塞埋張介紹比我<br />\n我愈聽愈唔耐煩飛返張紙比佢調頭就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實就係呢類人愈黎愈多<br />\n真係想人做問卷個d應該都食愈多檸檬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次先有個fd比人sell到簽埋約<br />\n無左2萬幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以真係小心啲 唔好比人呃到<br />\n而且我見做緊份工嘅多數係青年<br />\n年輕人 有咩驅使你正常工唔返 返埋d狗工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96e7e9cb4c4ea25ad8e02c39340d200a2bf8590","tid":893452,"uid":66887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27bea5a1d074ee18e4c739f398800d73092cbb42","tid":893452,"uid":199028,"like":153,"dislike":0,"score":153,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe5c33cb0327fe5faf68752b82fa9f1c56bfd0e","tid":893452,"uid":121247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:58:55.000Z","msg":"恒大畢業"},{"pid":"ea0aea36e81ee83687a39a347b04319dd28a244a","tid":893452,"uid":219941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:26:58.000Z","msg":"上次自己一個行旺角又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後上到去帶咗入啲房到，嚇死成個感覺係唔想俾你走，前面坐住一個人懶係真心想幫你，門口又企咗個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f11c7959a107f4b4965cb816e004c6222148da","tid":893452,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:04:03.000Z","msg":"點解香港仲會有人理街邊d sales<br />\n仲要跟埋人上樓<br />\n大佬呀唔好咁癲啦<br />\n2018年仲有呢d戇鳩仔<br />\n係咪太多時間好得閒 平時無人撩傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241db816d14e0bb89e240c04dd9f6b135cd57b9a","tid":893452,"uid":48492,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:13:03.000Z","msg":"次前有個呀伯表演雜技果條街<br />\n成日有班保險sales 做問卷<br />\n開場白一定係問有無食煙"},{"pid":"b22cafc3d3bd9b2c3fead052c067305bdaa7b0ae","tid":893452,"uid":211517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:16:29.000Z","msg":"利申：有中同做健身狗<br />\n一個月8皮野 淨係教你做健身"},{"pid":"8070a44820ed76880757bf79d3c395f7e14a77fd","tid":893452,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:18:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬坐監坐咗幾耐最近先出返嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afae406f2d6a83cb6b09189c082603837283975","tid":893452,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:18:43.000Z","msg":"對住班仆街唔使理佢地架<br />\n當佢哋唔存在得架啦<br />\n<br />\n次次見到都會俾人鎖定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而次次我都當睇唔到聽唔到"},{"pid":"5c5061d08f5adb35ce7bfa9dd1a24199aa76a38f","tid":893452,"uid":10351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77d759b2c57aefa77ca576ba00c35c8536c902c8","tid":893452,"uid":10621,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"其實諗落呢d 撚屌真係好仆街 <br />\n首先幫得人做問卷 多數都係唔識拒絕人 or 心軟果d 人 佢就利用你呢個弱點去sell 你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:22:44.000Z","msg":"係，再加埋係到扮曬可憐，利用埋你啲同情心"},{"pid":"5b43dad70ed582b3a38ea1e420d5927dfae7eae4","tid":893452,"uid":22409,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:25:19.000Z","msg":"成日有人係巴士站附近做問卷<br />\n得兩條問題 但係要你寫電話/email<br />\n寫咗個朋友嘅電話上去<br />\n之後有一排，個朋友經常收到傳銷電話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對唔住呀 以後唔敢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勿相認"},{"pid":"2f7d4ef317687eb38cadc7add71abe80c4ee6f69","tid":893452,"uid":32800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c5061d08f5adb35ce7bfa9dd1a24199aa76a38f","tid":